<div class="page-header">
  <h1 class="page-title">Log CTO (Use COC)</h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle">Record compensatory time off taken by employees</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-body" style="text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <i class="fas fa-calendar-check" style="font-size: 4rem; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1f36; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Coming in Phase 4
    </h2>

    <p style="color: #697386; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      This feature will allow HR Staff to log compensatory time off usage by employees.
      The system will automatically debit credits using FIFO (First-In, First-Out) logic.
    </p>

    <div class="info-box" style="text-align: left; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> <strong>What this feature will do:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.25rem; padding: 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #0c4a6e;">
        <li>Select an employee and enter CTO date(s) taken</li>
        <li>Enter hours used (in 0.5 hour increments)</li>
        <li>View employee's available balance before logging</li>
        <li>System automatically debits from oldest active credits first (FIFO)</li>
        <li>Prevent usage if insufficient balance</li>
        <li>Show detailed transaction history in ledger</li>
        <li>Track which certificates were used for each CTO</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>
        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Feature Locked
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

